query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  c.name as country,
  s.name as service,
  s.smshubCode,
  a.name as api,
  p.smshubPrice,
  p.ourPrice
FROM prices p
JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE s.smshubCode = 'ot'
ORDER BY a.id;
